awscc_databrew_project (Data Source)

Data Source schema for AWS::DataBrew::Project

Schema

Required

  • id (String) Uniquely identifies the resource.

Read-Only

  • dataset_name (String) Dataset name
  • name (String) Project name
  • recipe_name (String) Recipe name
  • role_arn (String) Role arn
  • sample (Attributes) Sample (see below for nested schema)
  • tags (Attributes List) (see below for nested schema)

Nested Schema for sample

Read-Only:

  • size (Number) Sample size
  • type (String) Sample type

Nested Schema for tags

Read-Only:

  • key (String)
  • value (String)
